The drip tray (A13) is fitted with a level indicator (red) (A12) showing the level of water it contains (fig. 20). Before the indicator protrudes from the cup tray, the drip tray must be emptied and cleaned, otherwise the water may overflow the edge and damage the appliance, the surface it rests on or the surrounding area.  
